## These files are for setting up a Formbot Voron 2.4 R2 350mm build

##Parts/Features Include:

#Meanwell LRS-200-24
    #No cooling fan

#Meanwell RS-25-5
    #No cooling fan

#BTT Pi Board
    #No cooling fan

#BTT Octopus v1.1 Controller Board
    #120mm Be Quiet (12v) Temperature controlled fan (58c)

#Stealthburner extruder assembly
    #Nema14 36mm (24v) motor
    #Clockwork 2 extruder gears
    #Revo Voron 40W (24v) hotend
    #Octotap v1.0 PCB (Z endstop probe) (nozzle 150c limit to homing)
    #Neopixel (3) index LEDS (GRBW basic)

#BTT_mini12864 (LCD display)
    #LED status colour changing

#XYZ Steppers
    #Moons Nema17 (24v) x6 @ (X x1, Y x1, Z x4)